	<h1 class="title">对于创意工作来说，致力免费分享的数字经济到底是敌是友？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3121/small/3121.jpg?1440471388" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Steven Johnson</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-26 08:05:12 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13948/medium/13948.jpg?1440470619" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13948" data-title="《对于创意工作来说，致力免费分享的数字经济到底是敌是友？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13948/medium/13948.jpg?1440470619" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13948.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
